The paper proposes a method for generating natural language explanations using a character-level recurrent neural network (RNN) model. This involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques, which are commonly associated with the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and deep learning (cs.DL). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
